items.label: Cascade
items.documentation: Delete the child records when the parent record is deleted.

items.label: NoAction
items.documentation: Prevent deleting a parent record as long as it is referenced.

items.label: SetNull
items.documentation: Set the referencing fields to NULL when the referenced record is deleted.

items.label: SetDefault
items.documentation: Set the referencing field's value to the default when the referenced record is deleted.
